<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="mean-adj">mean <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /miːn/    美 /miːn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>吝啬的；小气的：</strong></h4>
<p>反 generous </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He has always been <strong>mean with</strong> his money. 
他向来花钱小气。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>卑鄙的；刻薄的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is mean to speak ill of others. 
说别人坏话是卑鄙的行为。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A cyberbully uses the Internet to <strong>be mean to</strong> others.
网络恶霸使用互联网来欺负别人。</p><footer>人教新必修② – 3</footer></div></div>